ision series]]\n[[Category:2020s British television series]]\n[[Category:British television talk shows]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:ITV television programmes]]\n[[Category:Television series by ITV Studios]]\n[[Category:Television programmes produced by Granada Television]]\n[[Category:Television programmes produced by Anglia Television]]\n[[Category:Television production suspended due to the 2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]]\n", "text_old": "{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{Short description|British talk show}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{For|the film of the same name|Loose Women (film)}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Loose Women\n| image              = Loose Women logo (2019-present).png\n| genre              = [[Talk show]]\n| creator            = Diane Nelmes<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/oct/03/independentproductioncompanies.itv|title=Diane Nelmes joins Liberty Bell|first=Leigh|last=Holmwood|date=3 October 2008|via=[[The Guardian]]}}</ref>\n| presenter          = {{Plainlist|<!-- Please note that WP:TVCAST says that this listing should be ordered according to the original broadcast credits, with new cast members being added to the end of the list and that, as articles should reflect the entire history of a series, such actors remain on the list even after their departure from the series. Any addition to, removal from, or reordering of this list should be explained in an edit summary! -->\n* [[Kaye Adams]]\n* [[Ruth Langsford]]\n* [[Andrea McLean]]\n* [[Christine Lampard]]\n}}\n| starring           = {{Plainlist|<!-- Please note that WP:TVCAST says that this listing should be ordered according to the original broadcast credits, with new cast members being added to the end of the list and that, as articles should reflect the entire history of a series, such actors remain on the list even after their departure from the series. Any addition to, removal from, or reordering of this list