 rain days = 130\n| Jan snow days = 14\n| Feb snow days = 14\n| Mar snow days = 9\n| Apr snow days = 1\n| May snow days = 0\n| Jun snow days = 0\n| Jul snow days = 0\n| Aug snow days = 0\n| Sep snow days = 0\n| Oct snow days = 1\n| Nov snow days = 6\n| Dec snow days = 13\n|year snow days = 58\n| Jan humidity = 87\n| Feb humidity = 84\n| Mar humidity = 78\n| Apr humidity = 66\n| May humidity = 62\n| Jun humidity = 65\n| Jul humidity = 62\n| Aug humidity = 59\n| Sep humidity = 66\n| Oct humidity = 76\n| Nov humidity = 86\n| Dec humidity = 88\n|year humidity = 73\n|source 1 = Pogoda.ru.net<ref name=pogoda>\n{{cite web\n|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213144839/http://www.pogodaiklimat.ru/climate/34601.htm\n|archivedate = 13 December 2019\n|url = http://www.pogodaiklimat.ru/climate/34601.htm\n|script-title=ru:\u041f\u041e\u0413\u041e\u0414\u0410 \u0432 \u0417\u0430\u043f\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0436\u044c\u0435\n|publisher = \u041f\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0434\u0430 \u0438 \u043a\u043b\u0438\u043c\u0430\u0442\n|language = Russian\n|accessdate = 13 December 2019}}.  Snow days have been taken to mean days on which it snowed, not days with snow cover on the ground.</ref>\n|date= 3 August 2016\n}}\n\n==Governance==\n[[File:Zaporizhia Regional Administration.JPG|thumb|Zaporizhia Regional Administration building]]\n[[File:Zaporizhia City Administration.JPG|thumb|Building of the Zaporizhia city council]]\nZaporizhia is a regional seat of [[Zaporizhia Oblast]] and a city of regional significance meaning that it has a form of self-rule within the oblast (region).\n\n=== Administrative subdivision ===\nThe city is divided into 7 administrative raions.\n{| class=\"center\" \"toccolours\"  style=\"float:right; font-size:80%; margin-left:10px;\"\n|+ <big></big>\n| style=\"padding-left:1em;\" | <ol>\n<li>'''Oleksandrivsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Zavodsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Komunarsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Dniprovsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Voznesenivsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Khortytsky'''</li>\n<li>'''Shevchenkivsky'''</li>\n</ol>\n|[[File:\u0420\u0430\u0439\u043e\u043d\u044b_\u0417\u0430\u043f\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0436\u044c\u044f.svg|thumb|left|300px|'''Raions of Zaporizhia city''']]\n| <ol start=\"18\">\n</ol>\n|}\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Demographics==\n\n===City population===\nThe city population has been permanently declined since the first years of the state independence. In 2014\u20132015 the rate of the population decrease was \u22120.56%/year.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://population.city/ukraine/zaporizhzhya/|title=Zaporizhia \u00b7 Population|website=population.city}}</ref>\n\nIn January 2017, the city population equaled 750,685 inhabitants<ref>[http://database.ukrcensus.gov.ua/PXWEB2007/ukr/publ_new1/2017/zb_chnn_0117.pdf \u0414\u0435\u0440\u0436\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438]</ref>\nTotal reduction of the population of the city during the state independence was around 146 thousand people ( 2017\u20132018 years are not included in this estimation)\n\n[[File:Zaporizhia Population Chart.png|thumb|Zaporizhia Population Chart]]\n {|\n  |\n {| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width: 100%;\"\n  ! Year !! Population !! Source\n  |-\n  |1781||329||<ref name=meria.zp>[http://meria.zp.ua/test/index.php?id=5 ''Official Portal Zaporizhia city authorities, History'' (\u041e\u0444\u0456\u0446\u0456\u0439\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0430\u043b, \u0417\u0430\u043f\u043e\u0440\u0456\u0437\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0457 \u043c\u0456\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0457 \u0432\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438, \u0406\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0440\u0456\u044f \u043c\u0456\u0441\u0442\u0430)] {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/65BBXgL7l?url=http://meria.zp.ua/test/index.php?id=5 |date=3 February 2012 }}, accessed 11 April 2011. {{in lang|uk}}</ref>\n  |-\n  |1795||1,230||<ref name=meria.zp/>\n  |-\n  |1804||2,500||<ref name=meria.zp/>\n  |-\n  |1824||1,716||<ref name=Natalia/>\n  |-\n  |1859||3,100||<ref name=Natalia/>\n  |-\n  |1861||3,819||<ref name=meria.zp/><r